CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 31, 1941, pg. 7, reads: "[illegible] Woman's Day at Ebenezer Baptist Church... Charming visitors to Ebenezer Woman's Day, bottom right, Mrs. Harry Fitzgerald, Mrs. W. A. Jones Jr., Mrs. Cornell Talley. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Harry Fitzgerald holding child's hand, Mrs. W. A. Jones Jr., and Martha Talley, standing in street
